name: D/D/D Gust Emperor Executive Alexander
desc:
1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner monsters
While there are 3 or more "D/D/D" monsters on the field, this card gains 3000 ATK. If another "D/D" monster(s) is Normal or Special Summoned to your field, while you control this face-up card (except during the Damage Step): You can target 1 "D/D" monster in your GY; Special Summon it. You can only use this effect of "D/D/D Gust Emperor Executive Alexander" once per turn.
